name: VOXELFINE #1: "The Great Wave off Kanegawa" by Hokusai 3D voxelart model (.glb)
description: The original pixel art for this piece was made in memory of the first HEN swap exploit. It is a 3D voxel model of the original woodblock painting by Hokusai in .glb format. Voxelfines are ready to be imported into a VR or AR experience of your choice! By Lorem Ipsum, 2021.
